Rotate leaves of a perfect Church tree right by one.
[A,B,C,D] в†’ [D,A,B,C].

A Church tree folds over its structure:
  Leaf(x)   = О»n.О»l.l(x)
  Node(a,b) = О»n.О»l.n(a(n,l), b(n,l))
So Node(Leaf(A), Leaf(B)) = О»n.О»l.n(l(A), l(B)).

